level.heading: Inconsistencies with other laws.
level.text: ยง 11-690 Inconsistencies with other laws. If any provision of this chapter is inconsistent with, in conflict with, or contrary to any other provision of law, such provision of this chapter shall prevail over such other provision and such other provision shall be deemed to have been amended, superseded or repealed to the extent of such inconsistency, conflict or contrariety.
